title: Tufts Junior Wins 2015 Global Peter Drucker Challenge (Tufts University)
text: ( Source : Tufts University ) MEDFORD/SOMERVILLE, Mass. ( October 20 , 2015 ) -- Tufts University junior Khuyen G. Bui has won the 2015 Global Peter Drucker Challenge , selected from among 148 students from dozens of countries in an essay contest
